	<!-- message -->
	<p>IGS/Yantis isn't going any where - neither is PA... the difference is if Sony does it utilizing direct management of items being moved between accounts and charging directly to the account billing card, then it's 100% safe whereas you have to mail your money away to someone and pray they don't screw you via PA/Paypal.<br />
<br />
Since the fact is that people are going to continue to do this RL money trading for in-game items/gear/accounts - let Sony regulate, IMO.<br />
<br />
I voted Yes.</p>
	
	
	
