	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I say NO.  I don't think that SOE should get involved with RL money transactions for IG items.  They need every Rep point they can muster to keep this game going.  Personally, I would lose respect for SOE if they got involved with Yantis or even tried to put them out of business by selling the items themselves.  Thats just less people dedicated to getting this game fixed, and they need all the people they can get.<br />
<br />
This game is already filled with people that don't know how to play it at the higher levels.  I see no reason to encourage this.<br />
<br />
Spraggon<br />
Bristlebane</p>
	
	
	
	
	
