	<!-- message -->
	<p>I trust SOE more than Yantis.<br />
<br />
Plus, honestly, I find the whole idea of "trusting" a video game company to be a little weird. They are a business to make money, I trust them to do their best to make their company successful. As far as a personal trust relationship between me and them, why would I trust them? They're a corporation out to make a profit.<br />
<br />
Do you "trust" the company that makes your toaster?<br />
<br />
PS I think geared character moves was a great idea.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
