	<p>Seriously if Sony wanted to take care of Yantis they could in a heart beat.<br />
<br />
They use accounts to offer to Sell plat to yantis, soon as trade initiates. Ban the account buying the plat. Rinse repeat. Yantis will no longer risk accounts to buy the plat from folks to resell. No more plat selling.<br />
<br />
Step two. Buy low end gear from yantis again come trade time Ban accounts used for trading.<br />
As long as sony uses purchases less the 12.00 dollars per ban they break even with the monthly fee each of the new yantis account created to take over the trades.<br />
<br />
Of course then they will simply offer the same service and change the eula to state its an offence to offer the same services outside of SOE.<br />
funny how the eula states they can change it so if they wanted to they would.</p>
	
	
	
	
	
